for any sort of relationship.\

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Toggle:
\f1\b0 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 \'a0Now, don\'92t worry, folks, we\'92re fine. We mention this as part of being open and honest, and because it\'92s important in understanding where this shitty rabbit hole of animal torture can take you. It\'92s weird, and it\'92s foreign, and it\'92s dangerous. You walk that dark path because you have to, but you walk off it by retaining your honesty and dignity and integrity \'96 even when it\'92s dark all around. We\'92re talking about our own hard parts, here, because they happened and because that\'92s how we make sure we\'92re not going rotten at the core.\

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Fausty:
